pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                dir('java-maven-sonar-argocd-helm-k8s/spring-boot-app') {
                    sh 'mvn clean package'
                }
            }
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                // Add deployment steps here
            }
        }
    }
}

Save this in java-maven-sonar-argocd-helm-k8s/spring-boot-app/Jenkinsfile in your repo.

Alternatively, use this script in Jenkins "Pipeline" job:

node {
    stage('Checkout') {
        git 'https://github.com/Sairam9849/Jenkins-Zero-To-Hero.git'
    }
    stage('Build') {
        dir('java-maven-sonar-argocd-helm-k8s/spring-boot-app') {
            sh 'mvn clean package'
        }
    }
}
